    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students make a minor mistake carrying out their strategy.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Before the warm-up, pass back the cool down and work in small groups to make corrections.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>